description:
Create an ExecutionSnapshot type that bundles the immutable inputs and outputs of a single scenario run:

```ts
type ExecutionSnapshot = {
  configId: string | null;
  configuration: ConfigurationDocument;   // the exact config used for the solve
  request: SolveRequest;
  result: SolveResult;
  contributions: ResultContributionRow[];
};
```

This is the foundational type that all downstream work depends on. Place it in a new file (e.g. web/src/solver/executionSnapshot.ts or web/src/results/executionSnapshot.ts) and export it.

No behavioral changes yet — this is just the type definition.

